title: Win Rugby World Cup 2015 Italy v Canada match ball with MasterCard
text: As a Worldwide Partner of Rugby World Cup 2015, MasterCard is offering Telegraph readers the chance to win the match ball used in the Italy v Canada pool match in Rugby World Cup 2015. Enter this competition now for the chance to win this unique prize. To enter this fantastic prize draw, complete the form below before midnight on Friday, 25 September 2015: Online Form - Win Rugby World Cup 2015 Italy v Canada match ball with MasterCard telegraph.co.uk Follow @telegraph
